# Firewall default zones
Block
# incoming packets are rejected with "ICMP-HOST PROHIBITED" message.

Dmz
# use on computers on demilitarized zone.

Drop
# any packets are dropped and NO REPLY.

Exrternal
# use on external networks with NAT.

Home
# use on home networks.

Internal
# use on internal networks.

Public
# use on public area. default zone for newly created network.

trusted
# all network connections are accepted.

work
# use in work area.
